Clove-Black is a gothic theme for Cinnamon. It is a remix of dark-glass theme and Minty theme, with some additional modifications to extend, improve, and match color scheme. The panel background is inspired DarkCold's panel.

Clove-Black is compatible with Cinnamon 2.0

Please report issues or suggestions at:
https://github.com/mordant23/cinnamon-theme-clove-black/issues


----
----

INSTALLATION

Extract zip file and to the themes directory. That's usually /usr/share/themes/ for system wide installation or ~/.themes/ for a specific user.

Use Cinnamon Settings to choose the theme.
Restart Cinnamon by pressing "Alt+F2".
Type "r" and then press Enter.

----
----

CREDITS
Inclusion of authors in the Credits does not imply they endorse my work

Cinnamon Default Theme
---
Author: Cinnamon development team
url: http://cinnamon.linuxmint.com
License: GPL2

cinnamon.css in the Cinnamon theme used as the template for Clove-Black's cinnamon.cs


dark-glass
---
Author: half-left authored original theme. Not sure who ported it to cinnamon
url: http://gnome-shell.deviantart.com/gallery/28081982#/d36szax
License: GPL3

The assets (except for the ankh overview icons) and the color scheme (except where otherwise noted) were taken from the cinnamon port of half-left's Dark Glass theme.

Dark Cold
---
Author: OriginalSeed
url: http://cinnamon-spices.linuxmint.com/themes/view/16
License: GPL3

The panel background is inspired by Dark Cold's panel background. Dark Cold uses a background image. Clove-Black uses background-gradient properties.

Minty
---
Author: satya164
url: http://cinnamon-spices.linuxmint.com/themes/view/25
License: GPL3

The background for the .window-list-item-box property was used.

Ankh overview icon
---
Modified from the Ankh image in wikipedia at http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Ankh.svg
License:  Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 3.0 Unported

Wallpaper used in thumbnail.png
---
Author: lukaso_dasein
url: http://www.flickr.com/photos/lukaso666/5373484686/#
License: Attribution 2.0 Generic (CC BY 2.0)

Mordant23 (Author of Clove-Black)
---
Darkened Dark Glass Popup Menu hover property.
Added Dark Glass color scheme to notifications and modal dialogs.
Standardized the hover color scheme for Menu Favorite buttons and the various panel buttons.
Various other tweaks in the color scheme to match the various elements of the theme.

